    <item>
      <title>特朗普新一轮关税行动将冲击牛油果、汽车和甜椒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-s-new-tariff-blitz-to-hit-avocados-cars-and-bell-peppers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普即将对来自加拿大和墨西哥的商品征收 25% 的关税，并对来自中国的产品征收 10% 的关税，这一举措将对美国家庭产生影响，导致蔬菜、水果和汽车等多种商品的价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-s-new-tariff-blitz-to-hit-avocados-cars-and-bell-peppers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度呼吁抵制保护主义，削减关税以示行业信号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/shun-protectionism-india-signals-to-industry-with-tariff-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国对邻国和中国征收关税的背景下，印度财政部长周日表示，印度削减一系列商品进口关税的举措表明，印度工业不能依赖政府的保护主义措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/shun-protectionism-india-signals-to-industry-with-tariff-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 12:16:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>诺特称欧洲央行通胀目标已可实现，将允许放松利率刹车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/ecb-inflation-goal-in-reach-to-allow-taking-foot-of-rate-brake-knot-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员克拉斯·诺特表示，消费者价格增长回到欧洲央行的目标水平将使政策制定者不再通过利率来限制经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/ecb-inflation-goal-in-reach-to-allow-taking-foot-of-rate-brake-knot-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 12:08:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
